task.summary: Two new radio buttons added for Rials and Tooman conversion. Menu backed to the default condition!
Code for operation of radio buttons added but this must be improved!
Colors added to activities! Radio buttons removed due to confusion that they created! Done button added to soft keyboard. Some code added to handle this key!
mipmap folders added to hold launcher icons; icons moved from drawable<density> folders to their corresponding mipmap<density> folders. Manifest updated to reflect this changes.
activity_konvertor changed to meet UI design!
Some code for hiding soft keyboard added! About activity changed to meet design requirements.
Logo files for xxhdpi added! hint for TeNumber added.
Logos and icons for all screen sizes added!
AncestralNavigation added to about activity! Some changes in the manifest for AncestralNavigation. Supportv7 added to gradle; Not necessarily good but have to for Material design thing.
A State List added as well as necessary Image resources for btn_convert to have a pressed state! Color of main activity changed by a little. Old btn_convert icon removed.
Now keyboard will be hidden if user presses btn_convert!
